 I don't understand all the media hype about the "millions" the Menendez trial 
has cost the taxpayers. 
</P>
<P>
 Wouldn't the prosecutors, judge, and the court be paid anyway for whatever 
trial comes up next? They surely won't be fired. 
</P>
<P>
 BARBARA DECKER 
</P>
<P>
 Palm Springs 
