<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA020794-0067 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 011203 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 7, 1994, Monday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 1; Column 2 
